<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''高血壓'''（{{lang-en|Hypertension}}，high blood pressure）是[[動脈|動脈]][[血壓|血壓]]持續偏高的[[慢性病|慢性疾病]]<ref name="Nai2014">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=K21_AwAAQBAJ|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|date=2014-05-02|isbn=978-0-7020-5249-1|language=en|first=Jeannette|last=Naish|first2=Denise Syndercombe|last2=Court|title=Medical Sciences E-Book|pages=562|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220064742/https://books.google.com/books?id=K21_AwAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。高血壓一般沒有症狀<ref name="CDC2015">{{Cite web |title=High Blood Pressure Fact Sheet |url=https://www.cdc.gov/dhdsp/data_statistics/fact_sheets/fs_bloodpressure.htm |date=2015-02-19 |website=CDC |access-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306125631/http://www.cdc.gov/dhdsp/data_statistics/fact_sheets/fs_bloodpressure.htm |archive-date=2016-03-06 }}</ref>，不過長期高血壓為[[冠狀動脈疾病|冠狀動脈疾病]]、[[中風|中風]]、[[心臟衰竭|心臟衰竭]]、[[心房顫動|心房顫動]]、[[周邊動脈阻塞|周邊動脈阻塞]]、[[視力受損|視力受損]]、[[慢性腎臟病|慢性腎臟病]]及[[失智症|失智症]]等病症的主要危險因子<ref name="Lack2015">{{Cite journal|title=Global burden of cardiovascular disease and stroke: hypertension at the core|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25795106|last=Lackland|first=Daniel T.|last2=Weber|first2=Michael A.|date=2015-05|journal=The Canadian Journal of Cardiology|issue=5|doi=10.1016/j.cjca.2015.01.009|volume=31|pages=569–571|issn=1916-7075|pmid=25795106|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220070054/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25795106/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WHO2011">{{Cite book |url=http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2011/9789241564373_eng.pdf?ua=1 |title=Global atlas on cardiovascular disease prevention and control |first=Shanthi |last2=Puska |first2=Pekka |last3=Norrving |first3=Bo |date=2011 |publisher=World Health Organization in collaboration with the World Heart Federation and the World Stroke Organization |isbn=9789241564373 |edition=1st |location=Geneva |pages=38 |last1=Mendis |name-list-format=vanc |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140817123106/http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2011/9789241564373_eng.pdf?ua=1 |archive-date=2014-08-17 }}</ref><ref name="Hernandorena2017">{{Cite journal|title=Treatment options and considerations for hypertensive patients to prevent dementia|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28532183|last=Hernandorena|first=Intza|last2=Duron|first2=Emmanuelle|date=2017-07|journal=Expert Opinion on Pharmacotherapy|issue=10|doi=10.1080/14656566.2017.1333599|volume=18|pages=989–1000|issn=1744-7666|pmid=28532183|last3=Vidal|first3=Jean-Sébastien|last4=Hanon|first4=Olivier|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220064816/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28532183/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Lau2017">{{Cite journal|title=Modifiable Risk Factors and Atrial Fibrillation|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28784826|last=Lau|first=Dennis H.|last2=Nattel|first2=Stanley|date=2017-08-08|journal=Circulation|issue=6|doi=10.1161/CIRCULATIONAHA.116.023163|volume=136|pages=583–596|issn=1524-4539|pmid=28784826|last3=Kalman|first3=Jonathan M.|last4=Sanders|first4=Prashanthan|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305111546/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28784826/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- Cause and diagnosis -->
高血壓可以分為[[原發性高血壓|原發性高血壓]]和{{le|繼發性高血壓|Secondary hypertension}}<ref name="Lancet2015" />，其中有 90-95% 為原發性高血壓，意即肇因於生活型態或遺傳因素<ref name="Lancet2015" /><ref name="pmid10645931">{{Cite journal|title=Essential hypertension. Part I: definition and etiology|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10645931|last=Carretero|first=O. A.|last2=Oparil|first2=S.|date=2000-01-25|journal=Circulation|issue=3|doi=10.1161/01.cir.101.3.329|volume=101|pages=329–335|issn=1524-4539|pmid=10645931|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220070226/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10645931/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。會增加風險的生活型態為[[超重|超重]]、[[吸煙|吸煙]]、飲食含有過量[[食鹽|食鹽]]、[[咖啡|咖啡]]、[[糖|糖]]及喝酒<ref name="CDC2015" /><ref name="Lancet2015" />，剩下的 5-10% 是繼發性高血壓，肇因於其他病症如慢性腎臟病、[[腎動脈狹窄|腎動脈狹窄]]、[[內分泌疾病|內分泌疾病]]或是使用[[避孕藥|避孕藥]]<ref name="Lancet2015" /><ref name = "啟新健康世界-專業健康檢查/醫學健康促進_2021">{{cite web | title = 啟新健康世界-專業健康檢查/醫學健康促進 | url = https://www.ch.com.tw/index.aspx?chapter=ABB010201 | language = zh-tw | accessdate = 2021-12-03 | archive-date = 2022-02-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220220064842/https://www.ch.com.tw/index.aspx?chapter=ABB010201 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

<!-- Diagnosis -->
血壓分為收縮壓和舒張壓兩種，即為心臟跳動時{{le|肌肉收縮|systole}}或{{le|舒張|diastole}}時的測量值；收縮壓是血壓的最大值，舒張壓是血壓的最小值<ref name=CDC2015/>。大部分成年人在休息時的收縮壓在 100-130 [[毫米汞柱|毫米汞柱]]（簡稱為 mmHg），舒張壓是 60-80 毫米汞柱<ref name="AHA2017">{{Cite journal|title=2017 ACC/AHA/AAPA/ABC/ACPM/AGS/APhA/ASH/ASPC/NMA/PCNA Guideline for the Prevention, Detection, Evaluation, and Management of High Blood Pressure in Adults: A Report of the American College of Cardiology/American Heart Association Task Force on Clinical Practice Guidelines|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29133356|last=Whelton|first=Paul K.|last2=Carey|first2=Robert M.|date=2018-06|journal=Hypertension (Dallas, Tex.: 1979)|issue=6|doi=10.1161/HYP.0000000000000065|volume=71|pages=e13–e115|issn=1524-4563|pmid=29133356|last3=Aronow|first3=Wilbert S.|last4=Casey|first4=Donald E.|last5=Collins|first5=Karen J.|last6=Dennison Himmelfarb|first6=Cheryl|last7=DePalma|first7=Sondra M.|last8=Gidding|first8=Samuel|last9=Jamerson|first9=Kenneth A.|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220226183933/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29133356/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="EU2013">{{Cite journal|title=2013 ESH/ESC guidelines for the management of arterial hypertension: the Task Force for the Management of Arterial Hypertension of the European Society of Hypertension (ESH) and of the European Society of Cardiology (ESC)|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23771844|last=Mancia|first=Giuseppe|last2=Fagard|first2=Robert|date=2013-07|journal=European Heart Journal|issue=28|doi=10.1093/eurheartj/eht151|volume=34|pages=2159–2219|issn=1522-9645|pmid=23771844|last3=Narkiewicz|first3=Krzysztof|last4=Redon|first4=Josep|last5=Zanchetti|first5=Alberto|last6=Böhm|first6=Michael|last7=Christiaens|first7=Thierry|last8=Cifkova|first8=Renata|last9=De Backer|first9=Guy|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220303202536/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23771844/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。若血壓持續超過 130/80 或 140/90 毫米汞柱（收縮壓/舒張壓），有可能是高血壓<ref name="Lancet2015" /><ref name="AHA2017" />。兒童的判斷準則和成人不同<ref name="JNC8">{{Cite journal|title=2014 evidence-based guideline for the management of high blood pressure in adults: report from the panel members appointed to the Eighth Joint National Committee (JNC 8)|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24352797|last=James|first=Paul A.|last2=Oparil|first2=Suzanne|date=2014-02-05|journal=JAMA|issue=5|doi=10.1001/jama.2013.284427|volume=311|pages=507–520|issn=1538-3598|pmid=24352797|last3=Carter|first3=Barry L.|last4=Cushman|first4=William C.|last5=Dennison-Himmelfarb|first5=Cheryl|last6=Handler|first6=Joel|last7=Lackland|first7=Daniel T.|last8=LeFevre|first8=Michael L.|last9=MacKenzie|first9=Thomas D.|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220308173851/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24352797/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。量血壓時，採用 24 小時區間的{{le|移動式血壓計測量血壓|ambulatory blood pressure monitoring}}（簡稱為 ABPM）方式會較僅採{{le|診間血壓量測|Office blood pressure monitoring}}（簡稱為 OBPM）來得準確許多<ref name="Lancet2015" /><ref name="Nai2014" />。

<!-- Treatment and epidemiology -->
降低血壓和致命併發症的風險在於改變生活型態與藥物控制<ref name="NIH2015Tx">{{Cite web |title=How Is High Blood Pressure Treated? |url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hbp/treatment |date=2015-09-10 |website=National Heart, Lung, and Blood Institute |access-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406073903/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hbp/treatment |archive-date=2016-04-06 }}</ref>。[[減肥|减少体重]]、[[體能訓練|體能鍛鍊]]、適度{{le|攝取鹽份|Health effects of salt}}、少喝酒及[[均衡飲食|均衡飲食]]等方式都有幫助<ref name="Lancet2015" />，若改變生活型態也無效時，則應使用[[抗高血藥|抗高血藥]]<ref name="NIH2015Tx" />。目前多達3種藥物對九成人類的血壓控制上有效<ref name=Lancet2015/>，而以藥物治療第二期高血壓（收縮壓>160/100 mmHg），有望延長患者的預期壽命<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Pharmacotherapy for hypertension in adults 60 years or older|url=https://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/14651858.CD000028.pub3|last=Musini|first=Vijaya M|last2=Tejani|first2=Aaron M|date=2019-06-05|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=1|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD000028.pub3|editor-last=Cochrane Hypertension Group|volume=2020|language=en|pmc=PMC6550717|pmid=31167038|last3=Bassett|first3=Ken|last4=Puil|first4=Lorri|last5=Wright|first5=James M}}</ref>。但對於正常但偏高血壓及第一期高血壓（即130至160 mmHg）的患者而言，藥效相對不明朗，某些研究認為有效<ref name="AHA2017" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Effects of blood pressure reduction in mild hypertension: a systematic review and meta-analysis|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25531552|last=Sundström|first=Johan|last2=Arima|first2=Hisatomi|date=2015-02-03|journal=Annals of Internal Medicine|issue=3|doi=10.7326/M14-0773|volume=162|pages=184–191|issn=1539-3704|pmid=25531552|last3=Jackson|first3=Rod|last4=Turnbull|first4=Fiona|last5=Rahimi|first5=Kazem|last6=Chalmers|first6=John|last7=Woodward|first7=Mark|last8=Neal|first8=Bruce|last9=Blood Pressure Lowering Treatment Trialists' Collaboration|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220064919/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25531552/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |title=Effects of intensive blood pressure lowering on cardiovascular and renal outcomes: updated systematic review and meta-analysis |url=http://www.med-sovet.pro/jour/article/view/1765 |date=January 2016 |journal=Lancet |issue=10017 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(15)00805-3 |volume=387 |pages=435–43 |pmid=26559744 |vauthors=Xie X, Atkins E, Lv J, Bennett A, Neal B, Ninomiya T, Woodward M, MacMahon S, Turnbull F, Hillis GS, Chalmers J, Mant J, Salam A, Rahimi K, Perkovic V, Rodgers A |access-date=2019-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190416234426/https://www.med-sovet.pro/jour/article/view/1765 |archive-date=2019-04-16}}</ref>，但亦有其他研究認為沒有幫助<ref name="Diao2012">{{Cite journal|title=Pharmacotherapy for mild hypertension|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22895954|last=Diao|first=Diana|last2=Wright|first2=James M.|date=2012-08-15|journal=The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=8|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD006742.pub2|pages=CD006742|issn=1469-493X|pmid=22895954|last3=Cundiff|first3=David K.|last4=Gueyffier|first4=Francois|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220308112523/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22895954/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Blood pressure targets for hypertension in older adults|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/14651858.CD011575.pub2|last=Garrison|first=Scott R|last2=Kolber|first2=Michael R|date=2017-08-08|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=8|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD011575.pub2|editor-last=Cochrane Hypertension Group|volume=2017|language=en|pmc=PMC6483478|pmid=28787537|last3=Korownyk|first3=Christina S|last4=McCracken|first4=Rita K|last5=Heran|first5=Balraj S|last6=Allan|first6=G Michael}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Pharmacotherapy for hypertension in adults aged 18 to 59 years|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/14651858.CD008276.pub2|last=Musini|first=Vijaya M|last2=Gueyffier|first2=Francois|date=2017-08-16|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=8|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD008276.pub2|editor-last=Cochrane Hypertension Group|volume=2017|language=en|pmc=PMC6483466|pmid=28813123|last3=Puil|first3=Lorri|last4=Salzwedel|first4=Douglas M|last5=Wright|first5=James M}}</ref>。全球約16至37%的人口患有高血壓<ref name="Lancet2015" />，據信 2010 年全球死亡人數之中，有 18% 與高血壓有關，估計約 940 萬人<ref name="Camp2015">{{Cite journal|title=Using the Global Burden of Disease study to assist development of nation-specific fact sheets to promote prevention and control of hypertension and reduction in dietary salt: a resource from the World Hypertension League|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25644474|last=Campbell|first=Norm R. C.|last2=Lackland|first2=Daniel T.|date=2015-03|journal=Journal of Clinical Hypertension (Greenwich, Conn.)|issue=3|doi=10.1111/jch.12479|volume=17|pages=165–167|issn=1751-7176|pmid=25644474|last3=Lisheng|first3=Liu|last4=Niebylski|first4=Mark L.|last5=Nilsson|first5=Peter M.|last6=Zhang|first6=Xin-Hua|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220071754/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25644474/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!--'''高血压'''（{{lang-en|Hypertension (HTN)}}或{{lang|en|high blood pressure}}），全稱'''动脉高血压'''（{{lang|en|Arterial hypertension}}），是一种[[动脉|动脉]][[血压|血压]]升高的[[慢性病|慢性病]]。血压的升高使[[心脏|心脏]]推动[[血液|血液]]在[[血管|血管]]内循环时的负担增大。血压有两种，收缩压和舒张压，分别为心脏跳动时肌肉收缩（systole）或舒张（diastole）时的测量值。正常静息血压范围为收缩压90–139mmHg（最高读数）和舒张压60–89mmHg（最低读数）。血压持续等于或高于140/90毫米汞柱mmHg时则为高血压。

