=== 成人 ===
对18岁及以上人群的高血压的定义为收缩压和／或舒张压值持续高于公认的正常值（目前此值为收缩压139mmHg毫米汞柱、舒张压89mmHg毫米汞柱：请参见分类表（））。如果使用24小时血压监测数值及家庭自测数值时，则应使用较低的阈值（收缩压135mmHg或舒张压85mmHg）。<ref name="NICE127 full">{{Cite book |url=http://www.nice. org. uk/nicemedia/live/13561/56007/56007. pdf |title=Hypertension (NICE CG 127) |last=National Clinical Guidance Centre |date=August 2011 |publisher=[[National_Institute_for_Health_and_Clinical_Excellence|National Institute for Health and Clinical Excellence]] |accessdate=2011-12-22 |page=102 |chapter=7 Diagnosis of Hypertension, 7.5 Link from evidence to recommendations |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719203803/http://nice/ |archivedate=2013-07-19 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>最近的国际高血压指南也对高血压范围之下的血压情况进行了分类，以指出在正常血压范围内的较高血压亦存在的风险。JNC7（2003）<ref name="jnc7">{{Cite journal|title=Seventh report of the Joint National Committee on Prevention, Detection, Evaluation, and Treatment of High Blood Pressure|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14656957|last=Chobanian|first=Aram V.|last2=Bakris|first2=George L.|date=2003-12|journal=Hypertension (Dallas, Tex.: 1979)|issue=6|doi=10.1161/01.HYP.0000107251.49515.c2|volume=42|pages=1206–1252|issn=1524-4563|pmid=14656957|last3=Black|first3=Henry R.|last4=Cushman|first4=William C.|last5=Green|first5=Lee A.|last6=Izzo|first6=Joseph L.|last7=Jones|first7=Daniel W.|last8=Materson|first8=Barry J.|last9=Oparil|first9=Suzanne|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220308121809/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14656957/|dead-url=no}}</ref>将收缩压在120–139 mmHg和/或舒张压在80–89 mmHg的范围定义为临界高血压，而ESH-ESC指南（2007）<ref name="ESH-ESC">{{Cite journal|title=2007 ESH-ESC Practice Guidelines for the Management of Arterial Hypertension: ESH-ESC Task Force on the Management of Arterial Hypertension|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17762635|last=Mancia|first=Giuseppe|last2=De Backer|first2=Guy|date=2007-09|journal=Journal of Hypertension|issue=9|doi=10.1097/HJH.0b013e3282f0580f|volume=25|pages=1751–1762|issn=0263-6352|pmid=17762635|last3=Dominiczak|first3=Anna|last4=Cifkova|first4=Renata|last5=Fagard|first5=Robert|last6=Germano|first6=Giuseppe|last7=Grassi|first7=Guido|last8=Heagerty|first8=Anthony M.|last9=Kjeldsen|first9=Sverre E.|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220065026/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17762635/|dead-url=no}}</ref>及BHS IV（2004）<ref name="BHSIV">{{Cite journal|title=Guidelines for management of hypertension: report of the fourth working party of the British Hypertension Society, 2004-BHS IV|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14973512|last=Williams|first=B.|last2=Poulter|first2=N. R.|date=2004-03|journal=Journal of Human Hypertension|issue=3|doi=10.1038/sj.jhh.1001683|volume=18|pages=139–185|issn=0950-9240|pmid=14973512|last3=Brown|first3=M. J.|last4=Davis|first4=M.|last5=McInnes|first5=G. T.|last6=Potter|first6=J. F.|last7=Sever|first7=P. S.|last8=McG Thom|first8=S.|last9=British Hypertension Society|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220070325/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14973512/|dead-url=no}}</ref>以最佳、正常及正常高值细分收缩压低于140 mmHg及舒张压低于90 mmHg的组别。高血压也有如下分类：JNC7将高血压分为高血压一期、高血压二期和单纯收缩期高血压。单纯收缩期高血压指收缩压升高而舒张压正常，在老年人中常见。<ref name="jnc7" /> ESH-ESC指南（2007）<ref name="ESH-ESC" />和BHS IV（2004），<ref name="BHSIV" />将收缩压超过179mmHg或舒张压超过109mmHg的患者定义为高血压三期。如果[[药物|药]]无法将血压降低到正常水平，则此高血压为耐药性高血压。<ref name="jnc7" />

=== 新生儿及婴儿 ===
[[新生儿|新生儿]]的高血压很罕见，可见于约0.2－3%的新生儿；健康新生儿的常规检查不包括测量血压。<ref name="Dionne">{{Cite journal|title=Hypertension in infancy: diagnosis, management and outcome|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21258818|last=Dionne|first=Janis M.|last2=Abitbol|first2=Carolyn L.|date=2012-01|journal=Pediatric Nephrology (Berlin, Germany)|issue=1|doi=10.1007/s00467-010-1755-z|volume=27|pages=17–32|issn=1432-198X|pmid=21258818|last3=Flynn|first3=Joseph T.|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220065046/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21258818/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在高危新生儿中高血压则较为多见。在决定新生儿血压是否正常时应考虑多种因素，如胎龄（Gestational age），受孕龄和[[出生体重|出生体重]]等。<ref name=Dionne />

===儿童及青少年===
高血压在儿童及青少年中十分常见（按年龄、性别及种族不同，分别为2–9%）<ref>{{Cite journal|title=High blood pressure trends in children and adolescents in national surveys, 1963 to 2002|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17846287|last=Din-Dzietham|first=Rebecca|last2=Liu|first2=Yong|date=2007-09-25|journal=Circulation|issue=13|doi=10.1161/CIRCULATIONAHA.106.683243|volume=116|pages=1488–1496|issn=1524-4539|pmid=17846287|last3=Bielo|first3=Marie-Vero|last4=Shamsa|first4=Falah|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305223444/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17846287/|dead-url=no}}</ref>并被认为在长期可带来其它疾病的风险。<ref name="fourth">{{Cite journal|title=The fourth report on the diagnosis, evaluation, and treatment of high blood pressure in children and adolescents|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15286277|last=National High Blood Pressure Education Program Working Group on High Blood Pressure in Children and Adolescents|date=2004-08|journal=Pediatrics|issue=2 Suppl 4th Report|volume=114|pages=555–576|issn=1098-4275|pmid=15286277|access-date=2021-09-26|archive-date=2022-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220070422/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15286277/|dead-url=no}}</ref>目前的建议为三岁以上的儿童在进行常规医疗检查或治疗时应进行血压测量。应该在重复门诊测量确诊高血压后才定位儿童的高血压。<ref name = fourth />儿童的血压随年龄升高，儿童的高血压诊断标准为三次以上不同时间门诊测量的平均结果等于或高于此儿童相应性别、年龄及身高的95百分位血压。儿童高血压前期的定义为平均收缩压或舒张压大于或等于90百分位，但小于95百分位。<ref name="fourth" />

青少年的高血压和高血压前期诊断及分类建议使用成人标准。<ref name="fourth" />

==-{症}-状与体徵==
高血压很少显示[[症状|症状]]，因此通常是通过{{le|筛查 (医学)|Screening_(medicine)|筛查}}或者寻求解决其它健康问题时发现。一些高血压患者有[[头痛|头痛]]（尤其是后脑勺痛及早上头痛），并有[[头晕|头晕]]、[[眩暈_(醫學)|眩晕]]、[[耳鸣|耳鸣]]（耳中嗡嗡声或咝咝声）、视觉改变或[[昏厥|晕倒发作]]。<ref name="Fisher2005">{{Cite book |title=Harrison's Principles of Internal Medicine |last=Fisher ND, Williams GH |publisher=McGraw-Hill |year=2005 |isbn=0-07-139140-1 |editor-last=Kasper DL, Braunwald E, Fauci AS, ''et al.'' |edition=16th |location=New York, NY |pages=1463–81 |chapter=Hypertensive vascular disease}}</ref>

用[[体检|体检]]{{le|眼底镜检查|Ophthalmoscopy}}检查[[眼底|眼底]]时如检测到{{le|高血压性视网膜病变|Hypertensive retinopathy}}，则应怀疑患有高血压。<ref name="Wong2007">{{Cite journal |title=The eye in hypertension |author=Wong T, Mitchell P |date=February 2007 |journal=Lancet |issue=9559 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(07)60198-6 |volume=369 |pages=425–35 |pmid=17276782}}</ref>高血压性视网膜病变的严重程度传统上一般分为一期到四期，但程度较轻的分期之间可能很难互相区别。<ref name=Wong2007/>眼底镜检查结果也可以推断患者患高血压的时间长短。<ref name=Fisher2005/>
===原發性高血壓===
高血壓可以發生於任何年齡，但發現大多數是越過四十歲，約百分之八十五至九十屬於自發性高血壓，其引起原因並不清楚，可能與遺傳和環境因素有關。

===继发性高血压===
一些其它的症状及体征可以将诊断指向{{le|继发性高血压|Secondary hypertension}}，即由可确定的病因如[[肾脏疾病|肾脏疾病]]或[[内分泌疾病|内分泌疾病]]等引起的高血压。如胸腹部肥胖、{{le|葡萄糖不耐受|mpaired_glucose_tolerance}}、{{le|满月脸|moon face}}、“水牛背”及紫色{{le|皮纹|Stretch marks}}为[[库欣氏综合症|库欣氏综合症]]的症状。<ref name="ABC">{{Cite book |title=ABC of hypertension |last=O'Brien, Eoin; Beevers, D. G.; Lip, Gregory Y. H. |publisher=BMJ Books |year=2007 |isbn=1-4051-3061-X |location=London}}</ref>[[甲状腺疾病|甲状腺疾病]]及[[肢端肥大症|肢端肥大症]]也可以引起高血压，它们各有其特殊的症状和体征。<ref name="ABC" />腹部{{le|动脉杂音|Bruit}}可能表明[[肾动脉狭窄|肾动脉狭窄]]（肾脏的供血动脉变狭窄）。腿部血压降低或[[股动脉|股动脉脉冲]]的延迟或缺失可能表明{{le|主动脉缩窄|Coarctation of the aorta}}（距离心脏很近的主动脉狭窄）。具有变化很大的头痛、心悸、脸色苍白和出汗的高血压应马上及时怀疑是否患有{{le|嗜铬细胞瘤|pheochromocytoma}}。<ref name="ABC" />

===高血压危象===
极严重的血压升高（收缩压等于或大于180或舒张压等于或大于110，有时称为恶性或急进性高血压）称为「{{le|高血压危象|Hypertensive crisis}}」。血压达到这些数值之上表明并发症的风险很高。血压在此范围内的患者不一定有症状表现，但相较一般人群有较多出现（22%的病例）头痛<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Hypertension crisis |author=Papadopoulos DP, Mourouzis I, Thomopoulos C, Makris T, Papademetriou V |date=December 2010 |journal=Blood Press. |issue=6 |doi=10.3109/08037051.2010.488052 |volume=19 |pages=328–36 |pmid=20504242}}</ref>及头晕。<ref name=Fisher2005/>其它高血压危象的表现有心衰引起的视觉下降或呼吸困难，又或肾衰引起的感觉不适。<ref name="ABC" />大部分高血压危象患者已患有血压升高，但其它触发因素可能引起了突然的血压升高。<ref name="Marik2007">{{Cite journal |title=Hypertensive crises: challenges and management |author=Marik PE, Varon J |url=http://chestjournal.chestpubs.org/content/131/6/1949.long |date=June 2007 |journal=Chest |issue=6 |doi=10.1378/chest.06-2490 |volume=131 |pages=1949–62 |pmid=17565029 |access-date=2013-09-16 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20121204174126/http://chestjournal.chestpubs.org/content/131/6/1949.long# |archive-date=2012-12-04 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>

当严重的血压升高引起了一个或多个器官的直接损害时则为「{{le|高血压急症|hypertensive emergency}}」（以前称为「恶性高血压」）。损害可以包括{{le|高血压脑病|Hypertensive encephalopathy}}，即由脑部肿大和功能障碍引起的头痛和{{le|意识状态改变|Altered level of consciousness}}（意识模糊或嗜睡）。视网膜[[视神经乳头水肿|视神经乳头水肿]]、眼底出血和渗出是靶器官损害的另一迹象。[[胸痛|胸痛]]可能表明心脏肌肉损伤（可以进展为[[心肌梗塞|心肌梗塞]]），有时进展为[[主动脉剥离|主动脉剥离]]，即[[主动脉|主动脉]]内壁撕裂）、气促、咳嗽、咳血痰都是[[肺水肿|肺水肿]]的典型迹象。此病症的肺组织肿胀由[[心脏衰竭|左心室衰竭]]引起，即心脏[[左心室|左心室]]不能充分将血液从肺部泵入动脉系统。<ref name=Marik2007/>肾功能的急速退化（急性肾损伤）和微血管{{le|溶血性贫血|Hemolytic anemia}}（血液细胞的破坏）也可能出现。<ref name=Marik2007/>在这些情况，快速降低血压的目的是要停止正在进行的器官损害。<ref name=Marik2007/>相反在高血压急症没有出现靶器官损害迹象时，没有证据表明必须要迅速地降低血压。过度降低血压并不是没有风险的。<ref name="ABC" />在高血压急症时建议使用口服药物在24至48小时内逐渐降低血压。<ref name=Marik2007/>

===妊娠===
罹患[[妊娠高血压|妊娠高血压]]的孕妇约占怀孕孕妇的8–10%。<ref name="ABC" />患有妊娠高血压的女人，大多数在怀孕前就有原发性高血压。妊娠高血压可能是[[先兆子痫|先兆子痫]]的预兆，这是一种发生于妊娠后期和生产后几个礼拜的严重症状。<ref name="ABC" />先兆子痫的诊断可包括血压增高和尿蛋白。<ref name="ABC" />懷孕婦女約有5%機率會發生先兆子痫，而且约造成全球16%[[孕产妇死亡|孕产妇死亡]]。<ref name="ABC" />先兆子痫亦使宝宝的死亡风险提高两倍。<ref name="ABC" />先兆子痫通常没有症状，而且是由例行筛检检查出来。当发生先兆子痫的症状，最常见的就是头痛、视觉障碍（通常是出现闪光）、呕吐、上腹部疼痛和[[水肿|水肿]]（肿胀）。先兆子痫有时会演变为称之为[[子痫|子痫]]的致命病况。子痫是一种{{le|急性高血压|Hypertensive emergency}}，并且有数种严重的并发症。这些并发症包括丧失视力、脑水肿、[[强直阵挛性癫痫|癫痫发作]]或[[惊厥|惊厥]]、[[肾衰竭|肾衰竭]]、[[肺水肿|肺水肿]]和[[弥散性血管内凝血|弥散性血管内凝血]]（一种血液凝固功能障碍）。<ref name="ABC" /><ref name="urlHypertension and Pregnancy: eMedicine Obstetrics and Gynecology">{{Cite web |title=Hypertension and Pregnancy |url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/261435-overview |accessdate=2009-06-16 |author=Gibson, Paul |date=2009-07-30 |work=eMedicine Obstetrics and Gynecology |publisher=Medscape |archive-date=2015-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151115110917/http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/261435-overview |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===婴儿与儿童===
{{le|發育遲緩|Failure to thrive}}、[[癫痫发作|癫痫发作]]、焦躁不安、{{le|缺乏活力|Lethargy}}和[[婴儿呼吸窘迫综合症|呼吸困难]]<ref name="urlHypertension: eMedicine Pediatrics: Cardiac Disease and Critical Care Medicine">{{Cite web |title=Hypertension |url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/889877-overview |accessdate=2009-06-16 |author=Rodriguez-Cruz, Edwin |date=2010-04-06 |coauthors=Ettinger, Leigh M |work=eMedicine Pediatrics: Cardiac Disease and Critical Care Medicine |publisher=Medscape |archive-date=2013-06-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Hef8iyxf?url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/889877-overview |dead-url=no }}</ref>都与新生儿至三个月大的婴儿高血压有关。在三个月以上婴儿和儿童当中，高血压可引起头痛，不明的焦躁不安，[[疲倦_(医疗定义)|疲倦]]、{{le|發育遲緩|Failure to thrive}}、[[视力模糊|视力模糊]]、[[鼻出血|流鼻血]]和[[贝尔面瘫|面部神经麻痹]]。<ref name=Dionne/><ref name="urlHypertension: eMedicine Pediatrics: Cardiac Disease and Critical Care Medicine" />

==并发症==
[[File:Main_complications_of_persistent_high_blood_pressure.svg|thumb]]
高血压是全世界过早死亡最重要的可预防因素。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Global health risks: mortality and burden of disease attributable to selected major risks. |url=http://www.who.int/healthinfo/global_burden_disease/GlobalHealthRisks_report_full.pdf |accessdate=2012-02-10 |year=2009 |work=World Health Organization |archive-date=2012-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214111235/http://www.who.int/healthinfo/global_burden_disease/GlobalHealthRisks_report_full.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>高血压增加罹患[[缺血性心脏病|缺血性心脏病]]、<ref name="pmid12493255">{{Cite journal |title=Age-specific relevance of usual blood pressure to vascular mortality: a meta-analysis of individual data for one million adults in 61 prospective studies |author=Lewington S, Clarke R, Qizilbash N, Peto R, Collins R |date=December 2002 |journal=Lancet |issue=9349 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(02)11911-8 |volume=360 |pages=1903–13 |pmid=12493255}}</ref> [[中风|中风]]、<ref name="ABC" /> [[外周血管病变|外周血管病变]]、<ref name="pmid18375152">{{Cite journal |title=Management of hypertension in peripheral arterial disease: does the choice of drugs matter? |author=Singer DR, Kite A |date=June 2008 |journal=European Journal of Vascular and Endovascular Surgery |issue=6 |doi=10.1016/j.ejvs.2008.01.007 |volume=35 |pages=701–8 |pmid=18375152}}</ref>和其它心脏疾病的风险，包括[[心脏衰竭|心脏衰竭]]、[[主动脉瘤|主动脉瘤]]、廣泛性[[动脉粥样硬化|动脉粥样硬化]]和[[肺栓塞|肺栓塞]]。<ref name="ABC" />高血压同时也是罹患{{le|认知障碍|Cognitive disorder}}、[[痴呆|痴呆]]和[[慢性肾脏病|慢性肾脏病]]的高风险因素。<ref name="ABC" />
其它并发症包括：
*{{le|高血压性视网膜病变|Hypertensive retinopathy}}
*[[高血压肾病|高血压肾病]]<ref name="pmid19330604">{{Cite journal |title=Reactive oxygen species and dopamine receptor function in essential hypertension |author=Zeng C, Villar VA, Yu P, Zhou L, Jose PA |date=April 2009 |journal=Clinical and Experimental Hypertension |issue=2 |doi=10.1080/10641960802621283 |volume=31 |pages=156–78 |pmid=19330604}}</ref>

==病因==
===原发性高血压===
原发性（特发性）高血压是最常见高血压，占所有高血压病例90–95%。<ref name="pmid10645931" />在几乎所有当代社会中，血压會随着年齡而升高，而晚年罹患高压的风险也相当高。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Residual lifetime risk for developing hypertension in middle-aged women and men: The Framingham Heart Study. |last=Vasan |first=RS |date=2002-02-27|journal=JAMA: the journal of the American Medical Association |issue=8 |volume=287 |pages=1003-10 |pmid=11866648 |coauthors=Beiser, A, Seshadri, S, Larson, MG, Kannel, WB, D'Agostino, RB, Levy, D}}</ref>基因和环境因素可导致高血压。人们已发现许多对血压造成微小影响的常见基因，<ref>The International Consortium for Blood Pressure Genome-Wide Association Studies. Genetic variants in novel pathways influence blood pressure and cardiovascular disease risk. Nature 2011; 478: 103–109
doi:10.1038/nature10405</ref>还有一些对血压造成重大影响的罕见基因，<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Molecular mechanisms of human hypertension. |last=Lifton |first=RP |date=2001-02-23|journal=Cell |issue=4 |volume=104 |pages=545-56 |pmid=11239411 |coauthors=Gharavi, AG, Geller, DS}}</ref>但是对基因如何导致高血压，仍缺乏了解。有些环境因素也会影响血压。有助于降低血压的生活方式因素包括减少饮食中的[[食鹽|食鹽]]摄取，<ref>{{Cite journal |title=A comprehensive review on salt and health and current experience of worldwide salt reduction programmes. |last=He |first=FJ |date=2009 Jun |journal=Journal of human hypertension |issue=6 |volume=23 |pages=363-84 |pmid=19110538 |coauthors=MacGregor, GA}}</ref>多吃水果和低脂产品（也就是高血压防治饮食，例如[[得舒飲食|DASH飲食]]）。[[运动|运动]]、<ref name="ReferenceA">Dickinson HO, Mason JM, Nicolson DJ, Campbell F, Beyer FR, Cook JV, Williams B, Ford GA. Lifestyle interventions to reduce raised blood pressure: a systematic review of randomized controlled trials. J Hypertens. 2006;24:215-33.</ref>[[减轻体重|减轻体重]]<ref name="HaslamJames">{{Cite journal |title=Obesity |author=Haslam DW, James WP |journal=Lancet |issue=9492 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(05)67483-1 |year=2005 |volume=366 |pages=1197–209 |pmid=16198769}}</ref>和减少饮用含酒精饮料亦有助于降低血压。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Primary prevention of hypertension: Clinical and public health advisory from The National High Blood Pressure Education Program |author=Whelton PK, He J, Appel LJ, Cutler JA, Havas S, Kotchen TA ''et al.'' |journal=JAMA |issue=15 |doi=10.1001/jama.288.15.1882 |year=2002 |volume=288 |pages=1882–8 |pmid=12377087}}</ref>其它可能造成高血压的因素，例如压力、<ref name="ReferenceA" />摄取咖啡因，<ref>Mesas AE, Leon-Muñoz LM, Rodriguez-Artalejo F, Lopez-Garcia E. The effect of coffee on blood pressure and cardiovascular disease in hypertensive individuals: A systematic review and meta-analysis. Am J Clin Nutr. 2011;94:1113–26.</ref>以及维他命D不足，<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Vitamin D and hypertension: current evidence and future directions |author=Vaidya A, Forman JP |date=November 2010 |journal=Hypertension |issue=5 |doi=10.1161/HYPERTENSIONAHA.109.140160 |volume=56 |pages=774–9 |pmid=20937970}}</ref>则并未显示出与高血压有直接关系。[[肥胖|肥胖]]常见的[[胰岛素抵抗|胰岛素抵抗]]，是[[代谢综合症|X综合症]]（或称[[代谢综合症|代谢综合症]]）的致病因子之一，也被认为可造成高血压恶化。<ref name="pmid12364344">{{Cite journal |title=Obesity hypertension in children: a problem of epidemic proportions |author=Sorof J, Daniels S |url=http://hyper.ahajournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=12364344 |date=October 2002 |journal=Hypertension |accessdate=2009-06-03 |issue=4 |doi=10.1161/01.HYP.0000032940.33466.12 |volume=40 |pages=441–447 |pmid=12364344 |archive-date=2012-12-05 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20121205010228/http://hyper.ahajournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=12364344 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>近期研究亦指出，幼年时期发生的情况（例如出生体重过轻、母亲怀孕时抽烟、高PM<sub>2.5</sub>暴露<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Maternal Exposure to Ambient Particulate Matter ≤2.5 µm During Pregnancy and the Risk for High Blood Pressure in Childhood |url=http://hyper.ahajournals.org/content/early/2018/05/11/HYPERTENSIONAHA.117.10944 |last=Zhang |first=Mingyu |last2=Mueller |first2=Noel T. |date=2018-01-01 |journal=Hypertension |doi=10.1161/HYPERTENSIONAHA.117.10944 |pages=HYPERTENSIONAHA.117.10944 |language=en |issn=0194-911X |pmid=29760154 |last3=Wang |first3=Hongjian |last4=Hong |first4=Xiumei |last5=Appel |first5=Lawrence J. |last6=Wang |first6=Xiaobin |access-date=2018-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180519004205/http://hyper.ahajournals.org/content/early/2018/05/11/HYPERTENSIONAHA.117.10944 |archive-date=2018-05-19 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>和缺乏[[哺育母乳|哺育母乳]]）是成年原发性高血压的危险因子。<ref name="Lawlor 2005">{{Cite journal |title=Early life determinants of adult blood pressure. |last=Lawlor |first=DA |date=2005 May |journal=Current opinion in nephrology and hypertension |issue=3 |volume=14 |pages=259-64 |pmid=15821420 |coauthors=Smith, GD}}</ref>然而成人高血压的致病机制仍尚不明。<ref name="Lawlor 2005" />

===继发性高血压===
继发性高血压是由明确的病因所致。肾脏疾病是继发性高血压最常见的病因。<ref name="ABC" />而[[库欣综合征|库欣综合征]]、[[甲状腺亢进|甲状腺亢进]]、[[甲状腺功能低下|甲状腺功能低下]]、[[肢端肥大症|肢端肥大症]]、[[康恩氏综合症|康恩氏综合症]]、[[醛固酮增多症|醛固酮增多症]]、[[高胰島素血症|高胰島素血症]]<ref>Dankner, R., Chetrit, A., Shanik, M. H., Raz, I., & Roth, J. (2009). Basal-state hyperinsulinemia in healthy normoglycemic adults is predictive of type 2 diabetes over a 24-year follow-up: a preliminary report. Diabetes care, 32(8), 1464-1466.</ref>等内分泌疾病，也可导致高血压。<ref name="ABC" /><ref>Dluhy RG, Williams GH. Endocrine hypertension. In: Wilson JD, Foster DW, Kronenberg HM, eds. Williams Textbook of Endocrinology. 9th ed. Philadelphia, Pa: WB Saunders; 1998:729-49.</ref>其它病因则包括[[肥胖|肥胖]]、[[睡眠呼吸暂停症|睡眠呼吸暂停症]]、[[怀孕|怀孕]]、{{le|主动脉缩窄|Coarctation of the aorta}}、过度摄取[[甘草|甘草]]和某些处方药、草药疗方和非法药物。<ref name="ABC" /><ref>{{Cite journal |title=Drug-induced Hypertension: An Unappreciated Cause of Secondary Hypertension |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-medicine_2012-01_125_1/page/14 |author=Grossman E, Messerli FH |date=January 2012 |journal=Am. J. Med. |issue=1 |doi=10.1016/j.amjmed.2011.05.024 |volume=125 |pages=14–22 |pmid=22195528}}</ref>

==病理生理==
[[File:Arterial_pressure_diagram.png|thumb]]
大部份患有确立特发性（原发性）高血压的人，血流阻力（{{le|外周总阻力|total peripheral resistance}}）都因高血压而增加，而{{le|心排血量|cardiac output}}却维持正常。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Hemodynamic aspects of essential hypertension in humans |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_physiological-reviews_1984-04_64_2/page/617 |author=Conway J |date=April 1984 |journal=Physiol. Rev. |issue=2 |volume=64 |pages=617–60 |pmid=6369352}}</ref>有证据表明为何有些年轻人患有高血压或“临界高血压”而具有高心排血量，即心率加快，却有正常的外周血管阻力。这种症状被称为运动功能亢进临界性高血压。<ref name="Palatini">{{Cite journal |title=The role of cardiac autonomic function in hypertension and cardiovascular disease |author=Palatini P, Julius S |date=June 2009 |journal=Curr. Hypertens. Rep. |issue=3 |volume=11 |pages=199–205 |pmid=19442329}}</ref>这些人的心脏输出随着年纪的增长而降低，但外周阻力却随之上升，在老年时期发展成确立特发性高血压的典型症状。<ref name = Palatini />这是否是最后演变成高血压的人的典型模式尚无定论。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Prediction of future hypertension by casual blood pressure or invasive hemodynamics? A 30-year follow-up study |author=Andersson OK, Lingman M, Himmelmann A, Sivertsson R, Widgren BR |journal=Blood Press. |issue=6 |year=2004 |volume=13 |pages=350–4 |pmid=15771219}}</ref>确诊罹患高血压的患者其外周血管阻力增加，主要是由于小动脉和微动脉的缩窄。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Physiological aspects of primary hypertension |author=Folkow B |date=April 1982 |journal=Physiol. Rev. |issue=2 |volume=62 |pages=347–504 |pmid=6461865}}</ref>微血管数量或密度的降低亦可使外周阻力增高。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=The microcirculation and hypertension |author=Struijker Boudier HA, le Noble JL, Messing MW, Huijberts MS, le Noble FA, van Essen H |date=December 1992 |journal=J Hypertens Suppl |issue=7 |volume=10 |pages=S147–56 |pmid=1291649}}</ref>高血压也与外周血管弹性的减低有关，<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Arterial and venous compliance in sustained essential hypertension |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_hypertension_1987-08_10_2/page/133 |author=Safar ME, London GM |date=August 1987 |journal=Hypertension |issue=2 |volume=10 |pages=133–9 |pmid=3301662}}</ref>外周血管弹性减低会增加回流心脏的血量、增加心脏{{le|前负荷 (心脏病理学)|Preload (cardiology)|前负荷}}，最后导致{{le|心脏功能失常|diastolic dysfunction}}。发生的血管收缩是否为造成严重原发性高血压的原因之一，仍有待确定。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Reactivity of small blood vessels in hypertension: relation with structural changes. State of the art lecture |author=Schiffrin EL |date=February 1992 |journal=Hypertension |issue=2 Suppl |volume=19 |pages=II1–9 |pmid=1735561}}</ref>

患有高血压的年长者其{{le|脉压|Pulse pressure}}（心脏收缩和心脏舒张血压之间的差值）会越来越大。这种状况可能与心脏收缩压异常高但心脏舒张压却正常或异常低有关。这种状况就称为{{le|单纯收缩期高血压|isolated systolic hypertension}}。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Clinical practice. Isolated systolic hypertension in the elderly |author=Chobanian AV |date=August 2007 |journal=N. Engl. J. Med. |issue=8 |doi=10.1056/NEJMcp071137 |volume=357 |pages=789–96 |pmid=17715411}}</ref>患高血压或单纯收缩期高血压的年长者会有高脉压，可归因于[[动脉硬化|动脉硬化]]程度增高。这是种常见的老年并发症，而且可能会因高血压而加剧。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Mechanisms, pathophysiology, and therapy of arterial stiffness |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_arteriosclerosis-thrombosis-and-vascular-biology_2005-05_25_5/page/932 |author=Zieman SJ, Melenovsky V, Kass DA |date=May 2005 |journal=Arterioscler. Thromb. Vasc. Biol. |issue=5 |doi=10.1161/01.ATV.0000160548.78317.29 |volume=25 |pages=932–43 |pmid=15731494}}</ref>

高血压的动脉系统所见的血流阻力现象，有诸多致病机制予以解释。大多数证据指向下列两个病因或其中之一：
* 肾脏的盐和水调节紊乱，特别是肾内[[肾素血管紧张素系统|肾素血管紧张素系统]]异常。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Counterpoint: Activation of the intrarenal renin-angiotensin system is the dominant contributor to systemic hypertension |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-applied-physiology_2010-12_109_6/page/1998 |author=Navar LG |date=December 2010 |journal=J. Appl. Physiol. |issue=6 |doi=10.1152/japplphysiol.00182.2010a |volume=109 |pages=1998–2000; discussion 2015 |pmc=3006411 |pmid=21148349}}</ref>
* [[交感神经系统|交感神经系统]]异常<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Point: Chronic activation of the sympathetic nervous system is the dominant contributor to systemic hypertension |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-applied-physiology_2010-12_109_6/page/1996 |author=Esler M, Lambert E, Schlaich M |date=December 2010 |journal=J. Appl. Physiol. |issue=6 |doi=10.1152/japplphysiol.00182.2010 |volume=109 |pages=1996–8; discussion 2016 |pmid=20185633}}</ref>这些致病机制并不会彼此排斥，而是可能两者都在某种程度上造成大多数原发性高血压病例。人们也推测，[[內皮細胞功能受損|內皮細胞功能受損]]（血管内皮功能受损）和血管[[炎症|炎症]]，也可能使高血压里的外周阻力增加和血管损坏加剧。<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Endothelium-dependent contractions and endothelial dysfunction in human hypertension |author=Versari D, Daghini E, Virdis A, Ghiadoni L, Taddei S |date=June 2009 |journal=Br. J. Pharmacol. |issue=4 |doi=10.1111/j.1476-5381.2009.00240.x |volume=157 |pages=527–36 |pmc=2707964 |pmid=19630832}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |title=Role of the renin-angiotensin system in vascular inflammation |author=Marchesi C, Paradis P, Schiffrin EL |date=July 2008 |journal=Trends Pharmacol. Sci. |issue=7 |doi=10.1016/j.tips.2008.05.003 |volume=29 |pages=367–74 |pmid=18579222}}</ref>

